com.xilinx.rapidwright.device

Enum PIPType

  • Object
    • Enum<PIPType>
      • com.xilinx.rapidwright.device.PIPType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<PIPType>

    public enum PIPType
extends Enum<PIPType>
    This type captures the PIP properties shown in a Vivado PIP called "IS_BUFFERED_2_0", "IS_BUFFERED_2_1" and "IS_DIRECTIONAL"

    Vivado Tcl:

    report_property $pip

    Created on: Jun 9, 2015
